Summary The PR adds a SenseAudio speech provider to the bundled senseaudio plugin, including TTS and voice-list HTTP helpers, voice-note opus transcoding,      
registration metadata, docs, inventory updates, and tests.                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                
Reproducibility: not applicable. for the requested feature because current main simply lacks SenseAudio TTS. The remaining docs bug is source-reproducible from 
the PR docs line 95 and the current CLI contract requiring --provider <id>.                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                
